                </div>
<p>While the Z900 hasn’t undergone a complete overhaul, Kawasaki has made some <span class="font-weight-700">well-judged updates</span> to maintain its dominance in a competitive segment:</p>
<ul>
	<li>A new <span class="font-weight-700">color TFT display</span> with updated UI</li>
	<li>Slight updates to the <span class="font-weight-700">electronic rider aids</span></ li >
