<p><span class="font-weight-700">Updated Features:</span></p>
<ul>
    <li><span class="font-weight-700">New 5-inch full-color TFT display</span> with Bluetooth</li>
    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Rideology App support </span>for smartphone connectivity</li>
    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Three riding modes: </span> Rain, Road, Sport</li>
